Author: princess-kitty-belle
Text: I think denial is a really common part of eating disorders. I know I was in denial for a long while, even after being diagnosed for a while, and I've been in denial about how sick I was getting.

Author: Marianne22222
Text: You are not a loser You are still human, not despite, but With your disorder You just need time to accept your condition and overcome it, it surely won't be simple  but you're not less worthy because of it Your disorder does not define you
